  "html": "<div class=\"calumnia\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Etymology\">Etymology</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=calumnia&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Etymology\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><p>From <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Italic_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Proto-Italic language\">Proto-Italic</a></span> <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"itc-pro\"><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Reconstruction:Proto-Italic/kalwomni%C4%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Italic/kalwomni&#x101; (page does not exist)\">*kalwomni&#x101;</a></i>, from an unattested adjective <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"itc-pro\"><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Reconstruction:Proto-Italic/kalwomnos&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Italic/kalwomnos (page does not exist)\">*kalwomnos</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201C;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">deceiving, accusing</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201D;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>, from the same root as <i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/calvor#Latin\" title=\"calvor\">calvor</a></i>.\n</p><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Pronunciation\">Pronunciation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=calumnia&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Pronunciation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><ul><li><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content qualifier-content\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classical_Latin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Classica